creator: Corteva Agriscience
descriptionHtml:
Transform the way that you make decisions with Granular Link. It’s easy, powerful, and farmer-focused.

Join Granular Link and take advantages on the following benefits:

* Corteva knowledge at your fingertips. Simplify management and increase the profitability of your farm with the best available technologies and agronomist’s expertise.
* Precision farming. Be more sustainable creating variable rate application maps that increase the profitability of your farm and directly export them to your machinery.
* A new view of your fields. Monitor your farm using the most advanced vegetation indices on the market; track weather and irrigation needs anytime; identify field problems early to protect your yields.
* Stay linked. Work together with your Corteva Agronomist to get the most from your farm and to prevent any farming risk.
* Plan your daily activity. Save time focusing on what’s really important thanks to the personalized health ranking of your fields.

All in one place. We are integrating the best tools with the most advanced technologies from Corteva Agriscience to create personalized, accurate data-driven agronomy.

Download the app now FOR FREE and enjoy all Granular Link services.

Granular Link is a brand from Corteva Agriscience.
